<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/434832-currently-knee-deep-into-this-book-and-it">Currently knee deep into this book, and it took me a while to really understand it and get into it. Not very interesting at first, didn&#39;t capture my attention. After giving it several chances I&#39;m finally trying to finish just to get it over with. Not a book i recommend,but it has good writing and lots of hype. All in all, i still dont understand the point of the book?</a>
</div>
