<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/71129793-rachel-irvine"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_100x100-259587f1619f5253426a4fa6fb508831.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/71129793-rachel-irvine">Rachel Irvine</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    I think she was killed by a potion made up by the Apothecarist, but she wouldn't take it from him because she didn't know him, so the Apothecarist gav<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    I think she was killed by a potion made up by the Apothecarist, but she wouldn't take it from him because she didn't know him, so the Apothecarist gave it to the (child) grandfather and he gave it to her, not knowing what it was.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
